  </a>

  <!-- Profile Card Section -->
  <section class="profile-section d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
    style="min-height: 60vh; background: #f8fbff;">
    <div class="profile-card shadow-lg rounded-4 p-4 d-flex flex-column flex-md-row align-items-center"
      style="background: #fff; max-width: 700px; width: 100%;">
      <div class="avatar-wrapper me-md-4 mb-3 mb-md-0 text-center">
        <img src="ChatGPT Image Aug 6, 2025, 12_47_50 PM-min.png" alt="Profile Avatar" class="profile-avatar mb-3"
          style="width: 140px; height: 140px; object-fit: cover; border-radius: 50%; border: 6px solid #f4f8fb; box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);">
      </div>
      <div class="flex-grow-1 text-center text-md-start">
        <h2 class="fw-bold mb-1">Nidhi Kumari</h2>
        <div class="text-muted mb-2">@nidhi-webdev</div>
        <p class="mb-3">Crafting seamless digital journeys with Angular, JavaScript, React and a strong eye for UI. Based in
          Germany, passionate about turning ideas into clean, responsive, and meaningful web experiences.

        </p>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center justify-content-md-start align-items-center mb-3 gap-4">
          <div>
            <span class="fw-bold fs-4">12</span><br>
            <span class="text-muted">Repositories</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <span class="fw-bold fs-4">Berlin (Germany)</span><br>
            <span class="text-muted">Location</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="https://github.com/nidhi-webdev" target="_blank" class="btn btn-dark btn-lg rounded-pill px-4">View
          GitHub Profile</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- My Journey Section -->
  <section id="my-journey" class="py-5" style="background: #fff;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-5" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold;">
        <span style="border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.2em;">My Journey</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="row justify-content-center journey-cards-row">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mb-4">
          <div class="card journey-card shadow-lg rounded-4 p-4 border-0 d-flex flex-row align-items-center gap-4 position-relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="journey-logo-wrapper d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="min-width:110px;">
              <img src="extreme_networks_logo.jpeg" alt="Extreme Networks"
                class="journey-logo"
                style="width:90px; height:90px; object-fit:contain; border-radius:16px; box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(74,144,226,0.18); background:#fff; padding:10px; transition:transform 0.3s;">
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow-1">
              <h4 class="mb-1 fw-bold" style="font-family:'Georgia',serif; color:#4a90e2;">Extreme Networks</h4>
              <div class="text-muted mb-2" style="font-size:1.08rem; font-style:italic; letter-spacing:0.5px;">07/2022 – today</div>
              <p class="mb-0" style="font-size:1.07rem; line-height:1.7; color:#222;">Built UI modules for network monitoring and analytics using <span style="color:#e34c26;font-weight:500;">Angular</span> and <span style="color:#61dafb;font-weight:500;">React</span>. Enhanced performance and usability through real-time bug fixes and collaboration with cross-functional teams. Ensured responsive, accessible, and cross-browser compatible design.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="journey-card-accent" style="position:absolute;right:-40px;top:-40px;width:120px;height:120px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#4a90e2 60%,#fff 100%);border-radius:50%;opacity:0.12;"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-10 mb-4">
          <div class="card journey-card shadow-lg rounded-4 p-4 border-0 d-flex flex-row align-items-center gap-4 position-relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="journey-logo-wrapper d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="min-width:110px;">
              <img src="concentrix-logo.png" alt="Concentrix"
                class="journey-logo"
                style="width:90px; height:90px; object-fit:contain; border-radius:16px; box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(74,144,226,0.18); background:#fff; padding:10px; transition:transform 0.3s;">
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow-1">
              <h4 class="mb-1 fw-bold" style="font-family:'Georgia',serif; color:#f9a825;">Concentrix</h4>
              <div class="text-muted mb-2" style="font-size:1.08rem; font-style:italic; letter-spacing:0.5px;">08/2019 – 06/2022</div>
              <p class="mb-0" style="font-size:1.07rem; line-height:1.7; color:#222;">Delivered an accessible <span style="color:#e34c26;font-weight:500;">Angular</span> platform for NRS and TRS, enabling emergency communication for deaf and speech-impaired users. Developed reusable UI components, integrated secure authentication and real-time messaging, and ensured <span style="color:#4a90e2;font-weight:500;">WCAG</span> compliance. Collaborated with designers and Agile teams to deliver an inclusive, scalable solution.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="journey-card-accent" style="position:absolute;left:-40px;bottom:-40px;width:120px;height:120px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f9a825 60%,#fff 100%);border-radius:50%;opacity:0.12;"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-10 mb-4">
          <div class="card journey-card shadow-lg rounded-4 p-4 border-0 d-flex flex-row align-items-center gap-4 position-relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="journey-logo-wrapper d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="min-width:110px;">
              <img src="ernst-young-ey-logo.png" alt="EY Logo"
                class="journey-logo"
                style="width:90px; height:90px; object-fit:contain; border-radius:16px; box-shadow:0 4px 24px rgba(74,144,226,0.18); background:#fff; padding:10px; transition:transform 0.3s;">
            </div>
            <div class="flex-grow-1">
              <h4 class="mb-1 fw-bold" style="font-family:'Georgia',serif; color:#ffc107;">EY (Ernst & Young)</h4>
              <div class="text-muted mb-2" style="font-size:1.08rem; font-style:italic; letter-spacing:0.5px;">01/2019 – 08/2019</div>
              <p class="mb-0" style="font-size:1.07rem; line-height:1.7; color:#222;">Created frontend modules for GST filing and e-invoicing using <span style="color:#e34c26;font-weight:500;">Angular</span> and REST APIs. Built reusable UI components, optimized performance, and developed responsive dashboards. Enabled invoice validation and submission, ensuring cross-browser compatibility and seamless backend integration.</p>
            </div>
            <span class="journey-card-accent" style="position:absolute;right:-40px;bottom:-40px;width:120px;height:120px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#ffc107 60%,#fff 100%);border-radius:50%;opacity:0.12;"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Only Extreme Networks, Concentrix, and EY project cards remain -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

