  <!-- My Projects Detail Section -->
  <section id="my-projects-detail" class="py-5" style="background: #fff;">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="text-center mb-5" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif; font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: bold;">
        <span style="border-bottom: 2px solid #eee; padding-bottom: 0.2em;">My Projects Detail</span>
      </h2>
      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-10 mb-4">
          <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 border-0 d-flex flex-row align-items-start gap-4"
            style="background: #f8fbff;">
            <img src="extreme_networks_logo.jpeg" alt="Extreme Networks"
              style="width:90px; height:90px; object-fit:contain; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(74,144,226,0.15); background:#fff; padding:8px;">
            <div>
              <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">About Extreme Networks</h3>
              <p style="font-size:1.1rem;">Extreme Networks is a global leader in cloud-driven networking solutions,
                providing advanced network infrastructure and management for enterprises, data centers, and service
                providers. Known for innovation in network visibility, automation, and security, Extreme Networks
                empowers organizations to optimize performance and deliver seamless digital experiences.</p>
              <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Extreme_Networks" target="_blank"
                style="font-size:1rem; color:#4a90e2; text-decoration:underline;">Wikilink</a>
              <h4 class="mt-4 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Project Description</h4>
              <p style="font-size:1.05rem;">
                Extreme Cloud IQ is an advanced cloud-driven network management platform from Extreme Networks. It
                enables organizations to monitor, manage, and optimize wired and wireless networks from a single
                interface. With AI-powered analytics, automated troubleshooting, and real-time visibility, Extreme Cloud
                IQ helps enterprises improve network performance, security, and scalability. The platform supports
                seamless device onboarding, policy enforcement, and proactive issue resolution for global deployments.
              </p>
              <h4 class="mt-4 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Role And Responsibilities</h4>
              <h5 class="mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif; color:#888;">Role: Frontend Developer</h5>
              <ul style="font-size:1.05rem;">
                <li>Designed and implemented UI components for network monitoring and analytics dashboards using Angular
                  and React.</li>
                <li>Collaborated with backend teams to integrate REST APIs and real-time data streams.</li>
                <li>Optimized dashboard performance and responsiveness for large-scale network data.</li>
                <li>Resolved bugs and enhanced user experience through continuous UI improvements.</li>
                <li>Worked closely with product managers and QA to deliver high-quality releases.</li>
                <li>Partnered with clients and onsite stakeholders to gather requirements and align deliverables with
                  business goals, ensuring satisfaction with the end product.</li>
                <li>Actively participated in daily Scrum meetings to share progress, raise blockers, and engage in
                  collaborative problem-solving with the development team.</li>
                <li>Maintained cross-browser and cross-device compatibility, ensuring the application delivered a
                  consistent and responsive user experience.</li>
                <li>Developed reusable UI components to accelerate development and maintain consistency across modules.
                </li>
                <li>Implemented accessibility best practices to ensure inclusivity for all users.</li>
                <li>Documented technical solutions and provided knowledge transfer to team members.</li>
                <li>Monitored application performance and proactively addressed bottlenecks.</li>
                <li>Contributed to building and maintaining UI modules for network visibility, device monitoring, and
                  traffic analytics using Angular and React.</li>
                <li>Helped deliver scalable dashboards, interactive visualizations, and real-time troubleshooting tools,
                  improving customer satisfaction and reducing issue resolution time for global enterprise clients.</li>
              </ul>
              <h4 class="mt-4 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Technologies</h4>
              <div class="tech-tags mb-3">
                <span class="tech-tag html5">HTML5</span>
                <span class="tech-tag react">React</span>
                <span class="tech-tag angular">Angular</span>
                <span class="tech-tag js">JavaScript</span>
                <span class="tech-tag css">CSS3</span>
                <span class="tech-tag bootstrap">Bootstrap</span>
                <span class="tech-tag sass">Sass</span>
                <span class="tech-tag rest">REST API</span>
                <span class="tech-tag json">JSON</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-10 mb-4">
          <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 border-0 d-flex flex-row align-items-start gap-4"
            style="background: #f8fbff;">
            <img src="concentrix-logo.png" alt="Concentrix"
              style="width:90px; height:90px; object-fit:contain; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(74,144,226,0.15); background:#fff; padding:8px;">
            <div>
              <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">About Concentrix</h3>
              <p style="font-size:1.1rem;">Concentrix is a leading global technology and services firm powering the
                world’s top brands. Human‑centered, tech‑powered, and intelligence‑fueled, we design, build, and operate
                end‑to‑end enterprise solutions at speed and scale. Serving over 2,000 clients across 70+ countries, we
                blend data-driven innovation, AI, and human insights to transform customer experiences. With
                industry-leading platforms like iX Hello™, AI-powered conversational assistants, and comprehensive
                services from CX strategy to digital operations, we help businesses reimagine interactions and achieve
                seamless enterprise transformation.</p>
              <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Concentrix" target="_blank"
                style="font-size:1rem; color:#4a90e2; text-decoration:underline;">Wikilink</a>
              <h4 class="mt-4 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Project Description</h4>
              <p style="font-size:1.05rem;">
                The project involved developing an accessible web platform for the National Relay Service (NRS) in
                Australia and TRS in the Netherlands, empowering deaf, hard-of-hearing, or speech-impaired users to
                contact emergency services. The solution featured secure authentication, real-time communication, and
                intuitive UI components to ensure seamless access for all users. By prioritizing accessibility and
                reliability, the platform helped bridge communication gaps and deliver critical support to thousands of
                individuals.
              </p>
              <h4 class="mt-4 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Role And Responsibilities</h4>
              <h5 class="mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif; color:#888;">Role: Frontend Developer</h5>
              <ul style="font-size:1.05rem;">
                <li>Registered and logged in securely to access relay services when needed.</li>
                <li>Communicated with emergency services via a trained Relay Officer who relayed messages in real time.
                </li>
                <li>Developed seamless, cross-browser performance and accessibility through reusable UI components built
                  with Angular Material and PrimeNG.</li>
                <li>Enabled real-time data exchange and scalability using REST APIs, supporting thousands of users
                  nationwide.</li>
                <li>Designed a user-friendly interface for inclusivity and smooth operation, ensuring equal access to
                  public services.</li>
                <li>Delivered an enhanced user experience with a focus on accessibility, reliability, and ease of use,
                  ensuring everyone can access emergency services equally.</li>
                <li>Collaborated with UX/UI designers to enhance user experience and interface design.</li>
                <li>Participated in code reviews, providing and receiving constructive feedback to improve code quality.
                </li>
                <li>Worked in an Agile environment, participating in sprint planning, daily stand-ups, and
                  retrospectives.</li>
                <li>Documented development processes, code changes, and technical specifications for reference and
                  training.</li>
                <li>Ensured cross-browser compatibility and mobile responsiveness of applications.</li>
                <li>Conducted unit testing and integration testing to ensure software quality and reliability.</li>
                <li>Provided technical support and troubleshooting assistance for frontend-related issues.</li>
                <li>Kept up-to-date with emerging trends and technologies in frontend development and actively
                  contributed to knowledge sharing within the team.</li>
              </ul>
              <h4 class="mt-4 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Technologies</h4>
              <div class="tech-tags mb-3">
                <span class="tech-tag html5">HTML5</span>
                <span class="tech-tag js">JavaScript</span>
                <span class="tech-tag css">CSS3</span>
                <span class="tech-tag rest">REST API</span>
                <span class="tech-tag angular">Angular</span>
                <span class="tech-tag angular-material">Angular Material</span>
                <span class="tech-tag primeng">PrimeNG</span>
                <span class="tech-tag bootstrap">Bootstrap</span>
                <span class="tech-tag rxjs">RxJS</span>
                <span class="tech-tag typescript">TypeScript</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-10 mb-4">
          <div class="card shadow-sm rounded-4 p-4 border-0 d-flex flex-row align-items-start gap-4"
            style="background: #f8fbff;">
            <img src="ernst-young-ey-logo.png" alt="EY Logo"
              style="width:90px; height:90px; object-fit:contain; border-radius:12px; box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(74,144,226,0.15); background:#fff; padding:8px;">
            <div>
              <h3 class="mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">About EY (Ernst & Young)</h3>
              <p style="font-size:1.1rem;">
                EY is building a better working world by creating new value for clients, people, society, and the
                planet, while building trust in the capital markets. Enabled by data, AI, and advanced technology, EY
                teams help clients shape the future with confidence and develop answers for the most pressing issues of
                today and tomorrow. EY teams in more than 150 countries work across a full spectrum of services in
                assurance, consulting, tax, strategy, and transactions, strengthened by sector experience and diverse
                ecosystem partners.
              </p>
              <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ernst_%26_Young" target="_blank"
                style="font-size:1rem; color:#4a90e2; text-decoration:underline;">Wikilink</a>
              <h4 class="mt-4 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Project Description</h4>
              <p style="font-size:1.05rem;">
                DigiGST® is EY's flagship GST compliance platform, designed to help enterprises manage complex indirect
                tax processes in India. The solution automates GST return filing, reconciliation, and reporting,
                ensuring accuracy and regulatory compliance for large-scale organizations. DigiGST® leverages advanced
                data validation, secure integrations, and real-time dashboards to simplify tax workflows and reduce
                manual effort.
              </p>
              <h4 class="mt-4 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Role And Responsibilities</h4>
              <h5 class="mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif; color:#888;">Role: Frontend Developer</h5>
              <ul style="font-size:1.05rem;">
                <li>Developed frontend modules for return filing, e-invoicing, and data reconciliation using Angular and
                  REST APIs.</li>
                <li>Created reusable UI components with Angular Material, PrimeNG, and Bootstrap for consistent and
                  accessible user interfaces.</li>
                <li>Implemented virtual scrolling to optimize invoice loading speed, improving performance by 25% for
                  large datasets.</li>
                <li>Built dashboards to process and visualize high-volume tax data, ensuring fast and responsive user
                  experience.</li>
                <li>Integrated RxJS and TypeScript for efficient state management and reactive programming.</li>
                <li>Enabled businesses to file GST returns (GSTR-1, GSTR-3B), auto-fetch, edit, validate, and submit
                  invoices to government portals.</li>
                <li>Developed e-invoicing features for generating and registering invoices with the Invoice Registration
                  Portal (IRP).</li>
                <li>Designed reconciliation dashboards to compare buyer and supplier data, highlight mismatches, and
                  support corrective actions.</li>
                <li>Ensured accessibility, cross-browser compatibility, and mobile responsiveness across all modules.
                </li>
                <li>Collaborated with backend teams for seamless REST API integration and real-time data processing.
                </li>
              </ul>
              <h4 class="mt-4 mb-2" style="font-family: 'Georgia', serif;">Technologies</h4>
              <div class="tech-tags mb-3">
                <span class="tech-tag html5">HTML5</span>
                <span class="tech-tag js">JavaScript</span>
                <span class="tech-tag css">CSS3</span>
                <span class="tech-tag rest">REST API</span>
                <span class="tech-tag angular">Angular</span>
                <span class="tech-tag angular-material">Angular Material</span>
                <span class="tech-tag primeng">PrimeNG</span>
                <span class="tech-tag bootstrap">Bootstrap</span>
                <span class="tech-tag rxjs">RxJS</span>
                <span class="tech-tag typescript">TypeScript</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
